OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey pays tribute
OL,4,Cto 'our hero'
OL,6,FRob Burrow's wife Lindsey has called
OL,7,Fher husband "our hero" in a tribute
OL,8,Ffollowing his death at the age of 41.
OL,10,FLindsey, who became Rob's carer
OL,11,Ffollowing his diagnosis with motor
OL,12,Fneurone disease in 2019, said she was
OL,13,F"incredibly proud and fortunate to
OL,14,Fcall Rob my husband".
OL,16,FCountless tributes have been paid to
OL,17,Fthe former Leeds Rhinos player after
OL,18,Fhis death was announced on Sunday.
