OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey pays tribute
OL,4,Cto 'our hero'
OL,6,FIn his later years he became a
OL,7,Ftireless campaigner and fundraiser for
OL,8,FMND charities.
OL,10,FLindsey said: "I am unbelievably proud
OL,11,Fof the campaigning he's done to raise
OL,12,Fawareness and the millions of pounds
OL,13,Fthat have been raised in his name for
OL,14,FMND charities.
OL,16,F"I would like to thank the rugby
OL,17,Fleague community and everyone for
OL,18,Ftheir outpouring of love and support
OL,19,Fsince Rob's diagnosis. I truly
OL,20,Fappreciate every message of support,
OL,21,Fand fundraising that has been done."
