OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey pays tribute
OL,4,Cto 'our hero'
OL,6,FThe couple, who had three children,
OL,7,Fpublicly documented Rob's struggle
OL,8,Fwith MND and the impact it had on
OL,9,Ftheir family in an attempt to raise
OL,10,Fawareness of the condition.
OL,12,FLindsey added: "My priority is to make
OL,13,FRob proud, and to bring our three
OL,14,Fchildren up as Rob would want and
OL,15,Fensure their happiness and well-being.
OL,17,F"We will continue to keep Rob's legacy
OL,18,Falive. We will continue to bang the
OL,19,Fdrum and do our best to try and help
OL,20,Fothers."
