OL,3,CRob Burrow's wife Lindsey pays tribute
OL,4,Cto 'our hero'
OL,6,FShe paid tribute to medical staff who
OL,7,Fcared for her husband, adding:
OL,8,F"Although we knew this day would
OL,9,Farrive, I am somehow still feeling at
OL,10,Fa loss for words that our loving, kind
OL,11,Fand caring husband and father has
OL,12,Fdeparted.
OL,14,F"However, we take comfort from how
OL,15,Fmuch people's love and continued
OL,16,Fsupport meant to Rob through his most
OL,17,Fvulnerable times. He was simply the
OL,18,Fbest. Our hero."
